                Tickets can be purchased online, in person at the Gene Polisseni Center box office, or in person at the door. For members to get the reduced ticket price, they will need to buy their tickets at the Polisseni Center box office
            </p>
            <br>
            <h2 class="LansH2">Tournament List</h2>
